replies.body:
@Horse of Force

Cheers, at least I have an idea where they stand now. 

As for spending money on the game, I don't think I have any extra rights, my point is more that a lot of people spend a lot more money on lol than they would on any other game, because they love it so much. Other games manage to maintain an active set of admins who ban people, look into punishments properly and monitor the community, surely riot can do the same?
